      "originalText": "If you've wanted to learn vLLM but don't have a GPU sitting around, this is the path.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZsE1Bwjbe6iPkSlqNQzAV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -8005.580880724878,
      "y": -229.7945525578548,
      "width": 772.2001342773438,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "R96S2ecyxKazXddcYGpfj",
      "index": "c0ZEm",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 6661802,
      "version": 9,
      "versionNonce": 514465981,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784722573652,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Free Red Hat Developer Sandbox account.\nJupyterLab and models already deployed.\nYou connect, run the notebooks, and\nlearn by doing. No setup required.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Free Red Hat Developer Sandbox account. JupyterLab and models already deployed. You connect, run the notebooks, and learn by doing. No setup required.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "J-pGyofK0kdX9TrwhoCPo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -7995.680886828393,
      "y": -29.794552557854786,
      "width": 752.400146484375,
      "height": 270,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "R96S2ecyxKazXddcYGpfj",
      "index": "c0ZEmV",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1596780790,
      "version": 9,
      "versionNonce": 286463379,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784722573652,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In ~1 hour: quantize a model, serve it\nvia an OpenAI-compatible API, and\nbenchmark it under real load. The same\nend-to-end workflow you'd run in\nproduction, without the infrastructure\noverhead.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In ~1 hour: quantize a model, serve it via an OpenAI-compatible API, and benchmark it under real load. The same end-to-end workflow you'd run in production, without the infrastructure overhead.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
